### 10. 快速操作 Cheat Sheet

```bash
# ===== 改人设 =====
# 直接编辑即可，不用重启
vim ~/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/SOUL.md

# ===== 改 Key =====
# 编辑 openclaw.json 中的 env 字段，然后重启
vim ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json
openclaw gateway stop && sleep 3 && openclaw gateway install

# ===== 改模型 =====
# 编辑 openclaw.json 中 agents.list[x].model.primary，然后重启
vim ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json
openclaw gateway stop && sleep 3 && openclaw gateway install

# ===== 验证 =====
openclaw models status --agent <id>              # 检查模型和 key
openclaw agent --agent <id> -m "介绍你自己"       # 测试人设是否生效
openclaw channels status                          # 检查飞书连接
openclaw gateway status                           # 检查 Gateway
```
